{
  "stem": "23645.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've got to share this with some of the students and tell them it did happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if we don't watch, that it can happen again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let us go back to when you were in camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What kept you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Was it your belief in God?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't think much about this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, what kept me going is that I wanted to go home after it's all over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, in my mind, my perception was that my family's going to wait for me, because, you know, I was the kid-- the little kid-- and I wasn't going to make it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all worried about me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was going to march in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Surprise!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm alive!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you imagine that, when I wanted to do this, finally, and I found out there's no home to go home to and that everything that I've known, all the people that I played with, and all my family are gone, annihilated.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took a long time for me to come-- to get in touch with those kind of feeling and to-- and to come to terms with that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was most difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I'll tell you later on who was responsible to make us human again, because we weren't.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were dehumanized to such an extent that we began to believe it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were just a zombie, automatically doing the varied things to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, when the Russians started advancing, we thought, hang on!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're going to make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were marched out of Skarzysko, loaded on trains, packed like cattle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Off we went, deeper into Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People were dying left and right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have any food, nor drink.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
